{
  "id": "63abdc99572d31001e7b009c",
  "title": "散歩と思考",
  "created": 1672207516,
  "updated": 1672208767,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "63abdc99572d31001e7b009c",
      "text": "散歩と思考",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672207516,
      "updated": 1672207892
    },
    {
      "id": "63abde59aff09e000069aa4e",
      "text": "[歩行禅]の話を書いてから[散歩]を見たら散歩の思考に及ぼす影響の話題がいろいろ書かれてたのでそこだけまとめ直してみた[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672207962,
      "updated": 1672208049
    },
    {
      "id": "63abde59aff09e000069aa4f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672207962,
      "updated": 1672207962
    },
    {
      "id": "63abdc9caff09e000069aa0f",
      "text": "derived from [散歩]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672207516,
      "updated": 1672207534
    },
    {
      "id": "63abdd39aff09e000069aa1e",
      "text": "散歩します？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672207674,
      "updated": 1672207676
    },
    {
      "id": "63abdd39aff09e000069aa1f",
      "text": " 毎日してますね[sta.icon][dnin.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672207674,
      "updated": 1672207685
    },
    {
      "id": "63abdd45aff09e000069aa23",
      "text": " \t理由",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672207685,
      "updated": 1672207687
    },
    {
      "id": "63abdd45aff09e000069aa25",
      "text": "  \t哲学者[ソロー]に感化されてるから（歩いて[思索]に耽るのかっこいい",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672207685,
      "updated": 1672207698
    },
    {
      "id": "63abdd51aff09e000069aa26",
      "text": "  \t +1[tkgshn.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672207698,
      "updated": 1672207698
    },
    {
      "id": "63abdd51aff09e000069aa27",
      "text": "  \t 関連 [哲学の道]、[ペリパトス学派][nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672207698,
      "updated": 1672207698
    },
    {
      "id": "63abdd51aff09e000069aa28",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672207698,
      "updated": 1672207698
    },
    {
      "id": "63abdd3caff09e000069aa22",
      "text": "\t毎日川辺を歩いたり，大きな公園を散歩してます[erniogi.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672207677,
      "updated": 1672207748
    },
    {
      "id": "63abdd83aff09e000069aa2a",
      "text": "\t\t歩いているときに[降霊に成功] することが多々ある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672207748,
      "updated": 1672207751
    },
    {
      "id": "63abdd82aff09e000069aa29",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672207747,
      "updated": 1672207747
    },
    {
      "id": "63abddcbaff09e000069aa39",
      "text": "[増井俊之.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672207820,
      "updated": 1672207820
    },
    {
      "id": "63abddcbaff09e000069aa3a",
      "text": " 散歩してるときアイデアが出たことが無いので、軽い運動以外のメリットが感じられない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672207820,
      "updated": 1672207820
    },
    {
      "id": "63abddcbaff09e000069aa3b",
      "text": "  道や交通を気にしてると脳が発想モードにならない気が",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672207820,
      "updated": 1672207820
    },
    {
      "id": "63abddcbaff09e000069aa3c",
      "text": "  もっとボーっと歩くと良いのだろうか?",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672207820,
      "updated": 1672207820
    },
    {
      "id": "63abddcbaff09e000069aa3d",
      "text": "   コケそう...",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672207820,
      "updated": 1672207820
    },
    {
      "id": "63abddcbaff09e000069aa3e",
      "text": "  歩き慣れた道がいいと聞いたことがあります[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672207820,
      "updated": 1672207820
    },
    {
      "id": "63abddcbaff09e000069aa3f",
      "text": "\t\t私は（私も？）[ノイズが少ない道]じゃないと発想モードにならない感触があります[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672207820,
      "updated": 1672207820
    },
    {
      "id": "63abddcbaff09e000069aa40",
      "text": "　　確かに車の通る道ではなく川沿いの遊歩道とか公園の中の道とかを歩いてる時の方が思考に没頭できる[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672207820,
      "updated": 1672207820
    },
    {
      "id": "63abddcbaff09e000069aa41",
      "text": "　　 車の通る道を歩いてる時は特定のテーマをじっくり考えるというよりは無意識に空っぽになって、そこに奥深くからフワッと浮かび上がってくる断片的着想な感じ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672207820,
      "updated": 1672207820
    },
    {
      "id": "63abddcbaff09e000069aa43",
      "text": "\t\t関連 [インプットがないのが良い]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672207820,
      "updated": 1672208766
    },
    {
      "id": "63abe17eaff09e000000723a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672208767,
      "updated": 1672208767
    },
    {
      "id": "63abdcf0aff09e000069aa11",
      "text": "[yuki_minoh.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672207600,
      "updated": 1672207600
    },
    {
      "id": "63abdcf0aff09e000069aa12",
      "text": "　そういえば散歩好きな思想家・哲学者って結構いますよね",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672207600,
      "updated": 1672207600
    },
    {
      "id": "63abdcf0aff09e000069aa13",
      "text": "　古代ギリシャの哲学者たちは回廊を歩きながら講義をやったとか",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672207600,
      "updated": 1672207600
    },
    {
      "id": "63abdcf0aff09e000069aa14",
      "text": "　　[https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/逍遙学派 逍遙学派 - Wikipedia]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672207600,
      "updated": 1672207600
    },
    {
      "id": "63abdcfbaff09e000069aa1c",
      "text": "　　\t[逍遙学派] [ペリパトス学派]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672207612,
      "updated": 1672207622
    },
    {
      "id": "63abdcf0aff09e000069aa15",
      "text": "　[西田幾多郎]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672207600,
      "updated": 1672207600
    },
    {
      "id": "63abdcf0aff09e000069aa16",
      "text": "　　[https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/哲学の道 哲学の道 - Wikipedia] [哲学の道]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672207600,
      "updated": 1672207631
    },
    {
      "id": "63abdcf0aff09e000069aa17",
      "text": " [イマヌエル・カント]も散歩の逸話で有名",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672207600,
      "updated": 1672207600
    },
    {
      "id": "63abdcf0aff09e000069aa18",
      "text": " 　[https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/イマヌエル・カント イマヌエル・カント - Wikipedia]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672207600,
      "updated": 1672207600
    },
    {
      "id": "63abdcf0aff09e000069aa19",
      "text": " 「[歩くと思索が捗る]」というアイデアは少なくとも古今東西で見かける言明であるらしい？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672207600,
      "updated": 1672207642
    },
    {
      "id": "63abdcf0aff09e000069aa1a",
      "text": " 　万人に当てはまるのかは不明",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672207600,
      "updated": 1672207600
    },
    {
      "id": "63abdcf0aff09e000069aa1b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672207600,
      "updated": 1672207643
    },
    {
      "id": "63abdde8aff09e000069aa44",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672207848,
      "updated": 1672207848
    },
    {
      "id": "63abdde8aff09e000069aa45",
      "text": "[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672207848,
      "updated": 1672207848
    },
    {
      "id": "63abdde8aff09e000069aa46",
      "text": " [/nishio/散歩の効果]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672207848,
      "updated": 1672207848
    },
    {
      "id": "63abdde8aff09e000069aa47",
      "text": "  歩くことは発散思考も[収束思考]も高める、[発散]思考の方が高まる量は大きい",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672207848,
      "updated": 1672207848
    },
    {
      "id": "63abdde8aff09e000069aa48",
      "text": "  トレッドミルで屋内で歩いた場合や歩いてから座ってテストした場合も高まる #歩いてから座る",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672207848,
      "updated": 1672208077
    },
    {
      "id": "63abdde8aff09e000069aa49",
      "text": "  なので[nishio.icon]は「血流や酸素が増えて脳の働きが良くなる」と解釈してる #脳の血流",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672207848,
      "updated": 1672207929
    },
    {
      "id": "63abdde8aff09e000069aa4a",
      "text": " 公園の丸い道をぐるぐる歩いたり、行って帰ってくると5kmの遊歩道を歩いたり、状況によって使い分けてる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672207848,
      "updated": 1672207848
    },
    {
      "id": "63abdda2aff09e000069aa2e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672207779,
      "updated": 1672207817
    }
  ]
}